  subsequent revisions of this document after the operator runs
  <code>recupero-ops send-freeze-letters</code> and as issuer
  responses are recorded via
  <code>recupero-ops record-freeze-outcome</code> or the
  <code>POST /v1/freeze-outcomes</code> webhook endpoint.
</p>
<p class="small">
