    {% endif %}
    {% else %}
    Issue a preservation request to {{ issuer.name }}
    ({{ issuer.contact_email }}). As issuer, {{ issuer.short_name }}
    holds protocol-level authority over redemption and is the only party
    in a position to technically halt the {{ asset.amount_human }}
    {{ asset.symbol }} position at
    {% if current_holder.explorer_url %}<a class="mono" href="{{ current_holder.explorer_url|safe_url }}">{{ current_holder.address }}</a>{% else %}<span class="mono">{{ current_holder.address }}</span>{% endif %}. A request
    originating from your office is materially more enforceable than a
    third-party request.
    {% if issuer.kyc_required %}
    {{ issuer.short_name }} required full KYC at original subscription;
